description:
Indoctrinate U, Evan Coyne Maloney&#039;s much anticipated documentary exposing the anti-intellectual, intolerant culture of our nation&#039;s campuses, is finally here. And the film has been dubbed "a call to action" that will "shock the conscience of Americans in the best sense, through exposure to truth and logic." Now, just in time for graduation, the film America needs to see has arrived.
